          ],
          "associatedContents": [],
          "italics": [
            {
              "start": 116,
              "end": 121
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "Remember ye the law of Moses my servant, which I commanded unto him in Horeb for all Israel, with the statutes and judgments.",
          "footnotes": [
            {
              "footnote": "Ex. 19:7 (7–8).",
              "start": 49,
